</p>
<p>
7

A duk lokacin da dabarar function ya kewayo a aikinsa, to kuwa wancen wajen da
yake rike da bayanin da aka miko masa daga gurbi na uku shine kuma zai sake
dawowa ya shiga cikin tsarin dabarar da aka tsara. Misali. idan tun farko an shigo da
lambar 2 da 4 ne a wajen lissafasu kuma watakila a dabarar da aka tsara an sanya
cewa zai hada wadannan lambobi sannan zai ninka wadannan lambobi ko dai wani
abu kamar haka, to kuwa a duk sanda gurbin mika ‘parameters’ ya tashi mikowa to
kuwa wadannan lambobin zai yi ta mikowa ana maimaita wadannan lissafin da su a
wajaje daban-daban. Saboda haka; ya kamata kasan cewar za’a iya bada wakilcin
wasu lambobin ga wasu harrufan domin a duk sanda aka so amfani da wadannan
lambobin, to kuwa sai a kira wadannan harruffan su kuwa sai su miko lambobin da
aka wakilta musu ga gurbin zayyana dabaru da aka tsara, shi kuma sai yayi amfani
da wadannan lambobin domin aiwatar da dabarun da aka sanya masa yayi. To sai
dai fa ya kamata ka san cewar sharadin da zai bada damar mika wadannan harrufan
da suke wakiltar wasu lambobin to kuwa dolene sai wadannan harrufan nau’in
bayaninsu (data type) dolene sai ya dace da nau’in tsarin dabarar da aka tsara a
gurbin tsara dabaru.
Yanzu kam, na san ka dan fahimci yadda ake tsara dabarun function a yayin kirkirar
manhaja, sannan a gefe guda kuwa yana da matukar muhimmanci ka san cewar
akwai wani hanyar tsara dabarar function din kuma wanda baya bukatar ka zayyana
irin dabarun da zai maka kawai dai an riga da an sanya masa yadda zai aiwatar da
duk wata dabara da taimakon sanya sunan nau’in dabarar a farkon layikan umarni
na manhajar. Wadannan abubuwan kuwa sune ake kira da “Library functions”.
</p>
<p>
“LIBRARY FUNCTIONS” Ko mu kirasu da “AJIYAYYUN DABARU”: Wasu tsare-
tsaren dabarun functions ne da aka kirkiresu sannan aka sanyasu cikin tsarin
</p>
<p>
harshen kirkira (Programming language) domin ya bada damar amfani da su a wajen
aiwatar da wasu ayyukan na musamman domin ya samar maka da sauki a yayin
kirkirar manhajar ka. Kamar yadda nace kowane harshen kirkira yana zuwa ne da
irin nasa tsarin na ajiyayyun dabarun function domin yayin da ka sauke wani harshen
kirkira sannan ka bashi izinin fara aiki a cikin na’ura (install) to kuwa yana zuwane
tare da wadannan ajiyayyun dabarun functions a cikinsa.
Saboda haka; su ajiyayyun dabarun functions suna zuwane tare da kowane irin
harshen kirkira domin su amfaninsu shine suna dauke ne da wasu kalmomin umarni
iri-iri dama wasu dabarun na musamman masu kama da dabarun na functions domin
amfani da su a cikin manhaja.
</p>
<p>
8

Bayanin kowacce dabarar da ke cikin irin wadannan ajiyayyun dabarun gaskiya ya
wuce a yi shi a wannan dan littafin domin yawansa to amma dai ya kamata ka san
cewar a koda yaushe kana iya amfani da kowacce dabarar idan kaga dama. Saboda
haka dai; shi “library function” kamar wani tsari ne da yake tattare da wasu kalmomin
umarni ko na dabaru domin amfani da su a wajen samar da manhaja kuma kana iya
amfani da wasunsu tamkar yadda ake amfani da dabarar function.
A karshe dai, dangane da wannan batun, su Ajiyayyun kalmomi ko dabaru wato
“Library functions” wasu dabaru ne da aka kirkiresu sannan aka ajiyesu a cikin duk
wata harshen kirkira, kuma su basa bukatar a tsara ko a zayyana musu yadda zasu
aiwatar da wani dabara domin suna da nasu irin dabarun da aka riga aka sanya
musu zasu rinka aiwatarwa kawai idan kana son amfani da su sai ka sanya sunan
ajiyayyen dabarar (haeder file) da kake son ya aiwatar a farko sannan daga baya sai
ka yi amfani da kalmomin da suke kunshe a cikin wannan sunan dabarar.
Ga wasu kadan daga misalan wadannan ajiyayyun dabarun ko ajiyayyun kalmomin
kirkira da suke zuwa tare da harsunan kirkira:
printf(), scanf(), getch(), pow(), is_open(), close(), da sauransu.
Zaka yi mamaki idan aka ce maka za’a iya sanya wani dabara ya kira kansa da
kansa. Shin hakan zai yiwu kuwa? Amsar wannan shine E zai yiwu. Ai na san ma
kaga kadan daga misalin hakan a misalan da ya gabata a wajen tsara dabarun
function inda dabarar function ya kan tsallaka zuwa wani sashen layikan umarnin da
ya faro daga fari sannan ya sake kewayowa, to amma me kake gani idan aka ce
dabarar kansa ake son ya kira? to kuwa akwai wannan tsarin kuma shi ake kira da
“RECURSION” sai dai fa yana da kyau ka kula sosai a wajen tsara wannan dabarar
domin idan baka kula ba zaka yi mummunan dabara inda dabarar zai yi ta maimaita
kansa sau babu adadi (infinite recursive function).
“RECURSIVE” ko mu kirashi da “Dabara mai maimaita kansa”: Wani tsarin
dabara ne da yake iya kiran kansa da kansa. To amma idan ka dubi wannan dabarar
zaka iya cewar anya kuwa dabarar ba zai yi ta maimaita kansa ba babu tsayawa
domin duk sanda ya kai karshen dabarar zai sake kewayowane hakan zai yi ta yi.
Saboda haka yaya zamu magance wannan matsalar maimaitawa babu tsayawa? To
kuwa akwai mafita a wannan matsala kuma mafitar ita ce ake kira da “BASE CASE”.
Shi tsarin dabara mai maimaita kansa yana da bangarori guda biyu; bangaren da zai
yi ta maimaita kansa da kuma bangaren da za’a masa madakata ko matsaya wato
“Base case”.
</p>
<p>
9

. “Base Case” ko mu kirashi da “Madakata”: Wannan wani gurbi ne dake dakatar
da dabara da aka tsara domin yayi ta kiran kansa da kansa. Shi wannan gurbi tamkar
ma’aunine dake tabbatar da dabara ya dakata daga kewayowa matukar ya iso wani
ka’ida da aka sanya masa domin ya dakata. Domin a duk sanda dabara mai
maimaita kansa ya kewayo to kuwa wannan gurbin shine zai auna ya ga cewar shin
dabarar zai sake kewayowane ko kuwa a’a. sannan bangare na biyu kuma shine :
. Gurbin maimaita kansa (Recursive part): Wannan kuwa shine gurbin da zai yi ta
kiran kansa da kansa.
Ga misalai kamar haka:
